Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.07,0:00:03.77,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A racing second hand, a shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:07.24,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Conan's logic is the tonic\Nfor hearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.24,0:00:10.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's the Kaitō Kid special!\NDetective and thief square off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.85,0:00:12.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.65,0:00:14.52,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.52,0:00:16.93,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.17,0:01:40.10,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm high school student Shin'ichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.10,0:01:42.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I went with Ran Mouri, childhood friend and classmate,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:43.94,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}to an amusement park,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:47.51,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}where I witnessed a suspicious deal involving a man in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.51,0:01:52.41,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I was so engrossed with watching that I didn't see his partner hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:55.72,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I was knocked down and given a poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:01:59.39,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When I woke up, my body had shrunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:01.76,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If they learned Shin'ichi Kudo was alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:03.96,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}people around me would be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.96,0:02:06.93,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}After following Dr. Agasa's advice to conceal my identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:08.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran asked me my name and I quickly said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.43,0:02:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:14.87,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then, to uncover information about them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.87,0:02:18.60,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I moved in with Ran and her detective father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.37,0:02:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitō #1412?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! He's an older thief that all the young girls are crazy about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:40.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Older?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:42.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your dad's a detective and you never heard of him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.85,0:02:46.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean I love following crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:55.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you want my dad to catch this thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.23,0:03:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know Beika Museum's exhibit of world-famous jewels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Daddy submitted our family gem,\Nthe lucky Black Star pearl,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and wants it protected from Kaitō #1412's evil grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:13.90,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an8}Black Star
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why ask my dad and not the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't do that! The police would haul him off if they caught him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.26,0:03:29.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if your dad catches him, he might let us see his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.33,0:03:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Don't you wonder what he looks like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:37.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,#1412 has the entire world going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he's a fabulous guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.37,0:03:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like Harrison Ford or John Lennon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.38,0:03:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You live so happily...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.91,0:03:48.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The light's green, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:49.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:52.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be nice if he was like Brad Pitt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.33,0:04:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! The light's red!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, that was Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You sure it wasn't just a look-alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You passed by Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r} in Shibuya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.02,0:04:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he wouldn't respond! Isn't that horrible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:36.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, now! I wasn't in Shibuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:39.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And besides, I haven't even changed bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.40,0:04:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's probably sick of you.\NJust forget about that mystery dweeb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... He was walking with a girl, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:53.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was someone else! Don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.11,0:04:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:05:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, do they really want me to catch this Kaitō something-or-other?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitō #1412!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.32,0:05:08.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with the 1412?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.13,0:05:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one's really sure where it comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Sonoko, he steals art and jewels from all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:26.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,and his top secret FBI or CIA or Interpol number was 1412.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:31.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The leading theory is that people learned the number and it just stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.78,0:05:33.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sounds fake to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Apparently he has a different name in Japan, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:41.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably just word play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like "The Crazy Thief" or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:52.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think it was anything that old man-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:55.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How dumb. Who cares about some thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:03.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. I have a copy of a weird warning letter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.58,0:06:06.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that Kaitō #1412 sent to Sonoko's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A weird warning letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make any sense! It's like a code!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.46,0:06:16.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"April Fools."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When the moon splits the two,\NI shall enter upon waves"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"in the name of the black star."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.70,0:06:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Kaitō..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.34,0:06:26.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's torn here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Sonoko's father tore it up in anger when it arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.34,0:06:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then taped it back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:36.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, this makes no sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I do get is that "April Fools" means he'll show up on April 1st...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.19,0:06:45.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! I thought you went to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:45.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lemme see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.96,0:06:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:03.17,Character Card,,0,0,0,,March 31\NBeika Museum\N1:42 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.17,0:07:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:08.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like all the police in Tokyo\Nhave been mobilized...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess he really is a big international thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:17.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All that work and I still didn't break the code...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I truly appreciate your listening to my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:31.86,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shiro Suzuki (51)\NHead of Suzuki Industries
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're 100 men strong with a detective like you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Detective Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.17,0:07:39.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just one measly thief.\NI'll capture him with no trouble at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:44.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sure you will! You haven't even cracked the code yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is the largest black pearl in the world, the Black Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. The Suzuki family has been\Nblessed with prosperity
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,ever since my grandfather first purchased it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.46,0:08:00.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the family's guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:06.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Security sure is tight for the day before the theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:10.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. All we got from the letter was the date.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:14.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm told that security will be on full detail starting tonight—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's no telling from when\Nor where Kaitō #1412 will strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.48,0:08:21.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already told you! The river!\NDeploy men along the river bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:33.01,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shintaro Chaki (49)\NPolice Commissioner, Section 2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.13,0:08:34.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitō #1412 plans to sneak inside from the nearby Teimuzu River!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You cracked the code?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.27,0:08:42.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "enter upon waves" bit refers to the Teimuzu River!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.91,0:08:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Teimuzu River is the only place in the vicinity with waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,Teimuzu River
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,Beika Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:55.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you Mouri from Section 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.02,0:08:57.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're sloppy, Commissioner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.19,0:08:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Waves" means the ocean, which means "coast"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:02.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}oki
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And "star" means a pop star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the idol star who performs live tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,at the nearby Beika Town Hall, Yoko Okino{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's more, her last song will be "Moon Lady"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When the moon splits the two" means that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,Beika Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:22.64,Signs,,0,0,0,,Beika Town Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Kaitō #1412 will come from the vicinity of Beika Town Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.60,0:09:27.69,Signs,,0,0,0,,Beika Museum
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when the show ends at 9:00 pm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:31.11,Signs,,0,0,0,,Beika Town Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:33.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Whatever you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:35.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that does make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:38.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well done, Detective Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.36,0:09:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Have Teams C through E assemble near Beika Town Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:51.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Still, I haven't broken the code either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, where's the fellow who was transferred to us last month?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inspector? He took some officers somewhere this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:07.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's 2:00! Why don't we have lunch nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you guys gonna have lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We ate on the way here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:12.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute! Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.73,0:10:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.37,0:10:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Checking the direction with my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:27.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:31.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. First, you point the hour hand toward the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Japan's in the northern hemisphere, so halfway between it and 12
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.22,0:10:39.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is where south is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just testing something Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r} told me, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:52.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Which means south is at\N1 o'clock, and southeast at 2:30!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.08,0:11:01.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Aha! I've figured you out, Kaitō #1412!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:06.16,Character Card,,0,0,0,,March 31\N11:04 PM
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.05,0:11:11.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Fast asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agasa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:29.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shin'ichi! Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want me to find out about Kaitō #1412?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.65,0:11:37.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, Doc. He should be in my dad's crime files.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what do you need it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to know about him before I meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:47.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meet him?! You know where he is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:51.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup! I've figured out his route inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you tell the police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.00,0:11:56.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suddenly wanna see it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:12:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...the face of a retro thief who sends warning notices in this day and age!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The "two" in "when the moon splits the two"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}refers to a satellite and the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:18.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And if the splitting refers to the moon creating an eclipse between them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.46,0:12:23.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...then he'll show up between 12:30 and 4:00 am when BS TV is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:29.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes! The Black Star's initials are BS!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:29.56,Signs,,0,0,0,,Broadcast Satellite
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:34.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If the "waves" refer to a satellite signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:37.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...then he'll be coming from the direction of the BS signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.31,0:12:41.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The BS signal is sent from south to west at a 45° angle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:46.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and from 42.3° above the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:46.43,Signs,,0,0,0,,Haido City Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:53.01,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The only place that fits the bill is the roof of the Haido City Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! A strange kid ran into the hotel! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.87,0:13:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing. There's only one person I'm after.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.07,0:13:13.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And not even he could dress up as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:29.10,Signs,,0,0,0,,Employees Only
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:46.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Beika Museum is... right around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:50.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}12:28.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.92,0:13:53.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now I just wait for him to show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:14:00.06,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hi, Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I checked your dad's files with recent newspaper articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitō #1412 is enveloped in quite a bit of mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.63,0:14:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His first appearance was in Paris 18 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He suddenly disappeared 10 years later and was presumed dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:24.88,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but he's back after 8 years and is primarily active in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:29.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,18 years ago? He must be pretty old then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has all kinds of names...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The Modern Lupin," "The Moonlight Magician"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:40.20,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But there's one alias that people like the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alias?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A young novelist interested in the crafty Kaitō #1412
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,once jokingly read the number like so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"K I D."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.51,0:14:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"K I D?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:04.18,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right. Kaitō #1412 is known as...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:12.59,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...the Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He landed silently before me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.34,0:15:24.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so as not to disturb the stillness of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.01,0:15:29.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Together with a fearless smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}as if he saw through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:38.93,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's going on, Shin'ichi? Shin—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:49.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A cape and a silk hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An impenetrable stance...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.89,0:15:56.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't make out his face, but he's surprisingly young.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:16:01.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His thirties. Twenties? No, even younger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.33,0:16:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange flash and sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Above the Haido City Hotel, southwest of the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall I check it out, Commissioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course you shall!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:33.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! A helicopter! I think it noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems you're no ordinary kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.43,0:16:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Conan Edogawa. A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be escaping, Kaitō Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The helicopter will be here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:54.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I only have one chance to get him with my tranquilizer gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:57.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The instant he turns away to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A radio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chaki here! Kaitō Kid sighted on top of the Haido City Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:12.80,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Attention all patrol cars in Beika and Haido
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.80,0:17:16.30,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and all helicopters in the air above Beika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:20.58,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Proceed to the scene at once and capture the Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's using my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:25.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! That's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:29.92,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's his trap! All units, return at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.92,0:17:32.52,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is Helicopter #1! I'm above the hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.62,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sighting confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:35.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.71,0:17:38.72,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I think he sent the orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:42.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:45.35,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Attention all officers inside the Haido City Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Kid's on the roof! Rush to the scene at once! Seize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This guy's incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:55.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He can imitate any voice without a machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.61,0:17:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your voice is on the radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.21,0:18:04.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the Kid! He's using my voice to bring us to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.32,0:18:04.29,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ginzo Nakamori (41)\NPolice Inspector, Section 2
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's insane! Why on earth would he do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.72,0:18:10.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:19.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satisfied, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Freeze, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:27.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my. Inspector Nakamori. You certainly arrived quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:34.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ha! You knew I cracked your code and had the place staked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:38.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured you might hang-glide in, so I checked everyone in the hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.69,0:18:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and fortified the main entrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I never expected you to go around Tohto Tower and then land here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget about the pearl! You have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm only here to observe you tonight. I don't plan to steal anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:19:01.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? I clearly wrote so at the start of the letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:05.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"April Fools." It was a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.28,0:19:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let him escape! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A flash grenade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you aware, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A phantom thief is a creative artist\Nwho skillfully steals his prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:20.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}kaitō
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.36,0:19:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but a detective is nothing more than a critic
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who finds fault in what is left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:32.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:34.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:36.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.25,0:19:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Helicopters! Track him using radar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It only shows our three helicopters in the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has he gotten away again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:53.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is insane! No one can just disappear like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"On April 19th, I will appear on the Queen Selizabeth"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.17,0:20:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"leaving from Yokohama Port to steal the real Black Star."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"—Kaitō Kid"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:16.67,Character Card,,0,0,0,,April 19th\NQueen Selizabeth, Yokohama Port
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.05,0:20:16.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please cancel it, Commissioner Chaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with the Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't let him get near the jewel with such lousy security as that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.29,0:20:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that, Nakamori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight's party is full of important people!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't do anything rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, we'll lose face if we cancel the party out of fear of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.27,0:20:42.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. It'll take three hours for the ship to get to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.71,0:20:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a floating prison! Even if he does get on, he's like a rat in a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:55.08,Signs,,0,0,0,,Suzuki Industries 60th Anniversary Boat Party
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:55.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This year marks Suzuki Industries' 60th anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.42,0:20:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is entirely because of the support from you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.96,0:21:02.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please forget about sneak thieves for tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and enjoy this elegant and grand party\Nto which 500 have been invited!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.77,0:21:20.03,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tomoko Suzuki (43)\NSonoko's Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.98,0:21:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have devised a special plan for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.28,0:21:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please open the small boxes given to you before you boarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.05,0:21:27.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are my letter of challenge to any foolish thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:29.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.56,0:21:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! These are our family's symbol,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.66,0:21:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as well as the Kaitō Kid's prey tonight! The Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:43.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only one is real, of course.\NAnd only I know to whom it was given.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.10,0:21:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rest are imitation pearls!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:50.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, then. Please put them on your chests
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.85,0:21:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and tell the Kid, "Go ahead and take it, if you dare!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:22:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's assuming he manages to determine which one is real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,during the three hours we're at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.56,0:22:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your mom's pretty smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.46,0:22:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.02,0:22:11.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't find my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:13.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me she's still at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.41,0:22:19.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! The ship already left?! How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.71,0:22:19.38,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Suzuki Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my line! Do you know what time it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the commissioner called\Nto say he was delaying it 2 hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.28,0:22:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.39,0:22:32.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Daddy's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:33.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did the company president go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went to the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.67,0:22:51.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now I see! He got on board disguised as the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.67,0:22:54.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I thank you, Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.68,0:23:00.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You've given me a chance to tear off that bold mask of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.44,0:23:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! Kaitō #1412 disguised himself as Daddy to get on the ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.71,0:23:21.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just found his disguise and props in the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.42,0:23:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The officers are checking it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.78,0:23:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.32,0:23:30.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But this is him. I doubt they'll find any evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where's Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.73,0:23:36.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out looking for you, since you didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was worried Kaitō #1412 had caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not "#1412".
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:50.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Kaitō Kid! Get it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:51.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.02,0:23:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.15,0:24:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Nakamori. He works full-time pursuing the Kaitō Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.49,0:24:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like you, he's a reliable knight we hired to protect the Black Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.30,0:24:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All 500 people here are wearing black pearls!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.97,0:24:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And except for the real one, they're all imitations!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.78,0:24:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't guard it unless I know which one is real...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.28,0:24:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They all look alike, but they're still imitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.82,0:24:34.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Close scrutiny could narrow it down a bit;
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.46,0:24:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,among them are dull and dreary ones such as mine
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.56,0:24:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and excessively shiny rubbish such as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.57,0:24:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But checking every person in this crowd would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.21,0:24:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll give you a special hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.14,0:24:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Black Star, the black pearl with a peacock-green luster
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.75,0:25:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that fascinated my grandfather 60 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.88,0:25:05.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is with someone especially worthy of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.65,0:25:07.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Worthy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.72,0:25:12.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coincidentally, that someone is one out of five hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.89,0:25:16.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must be a woman, if the jewel suits them...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.43,0:25:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it suits you, too, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.57,0:25:21.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.73,0:25:26.23,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Joji Hatamoto (41)\NFrench Restaurant Chef
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.87,0:25:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's good to see you again!\NThank you for your help a while back!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.84,0:25:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you the Hatamoto Group's—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.44,0:25:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! Thanks to this fine woman\Nand the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.85,0:25:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've opened up more restaurants!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.65,0:25:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, tonight's meal is my own—
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.27,0:25:39.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So sorry, Joji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.95,0:25:45.67,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Takuya Mifune (26)\NPresident of Mifune Electronics
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.99,0:25:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems Mr. Suzuki won't be there,\Nthanks to the Kaitō Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.03,0:25:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your flattery food will go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.00,0:25:49.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're as reprehensible as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.35,0:25:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.60,0:25:55.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy from the Yotsui girl's birthday party...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:57.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? You're not wearing yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.90,0:26:01.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate childish games like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.38,0:26:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you'll seem suspicious if you don't wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.11,0:26:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.02,0:26:11.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Ayako{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.86,0:26:17.03,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yuzo Tomizawa (28)\NSonoko's Sister's Fiancée
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.89,0:26:14.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, she couldn't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.42,0:26:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh. That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.36,0:26:20.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is the Suzuki Industries party, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.40,0:26:23.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's teeming with rich kids and company presidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.43,0:26:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's taking a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.44,0:26:31.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's probably lost somewhere!\NRan has no sense of direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.11,0:26:33.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who has no sense of direction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.58,0:26:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ran! I didn't see you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.91,0:26:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Police Commissioner Chaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.58,0:26:41.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may have already heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.35,0:26:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that pesky villain has somehow boarded the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.99,0:26:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you know, he's a master of disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.76,0:26:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He possesses an immeasurable evil talent that he uses
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.79,0:26:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to learn about his target and fully imitate them,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.03,0:26:59.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even down to their face, voice, and personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.60,0:27:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He may even be among you already!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.94,0:27:09.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Normally, we would carefully inspect each and every person,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.08,0:27:12.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but we'll refrain from such incivility here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.61,0:27:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passwords!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.72,0:27:18.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pair up with the person next to you and decide on a password!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.32,0:27:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it! That way he can't keep disguising himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.73,0:27:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which will allow the police to single him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.10,0:27:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should our password be?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.57,0:27:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK, when I say "Holmes"...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.10,0:27:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...I'll say "Lupin"!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.34,0:27:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing, Power Room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.70,0:27:46.18,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, this is—
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.45,0:27:50.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.79,0:27:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your passwords are pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.68,0:27:54.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.99,0:27:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Black Star is already in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.99,0:28:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.90,0:28:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, dear. It's the pesky thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.93,0:28:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to punish this scheming boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.21,0:28:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.25,0:28:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.28,0:28:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry, Inspector. After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.96,0:28:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.83,0:28:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My guards caught him in the tablecloth
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.00,0:28:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after I pretended to shoot him\Nwith this model gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.07,0:28:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. He's a brilliant magician I hired as entertainment...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.41,0:28:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...Kazumi Sanada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.68,0:28:48.43,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kazumi Sanada (27)\NMagician
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.64,0:28:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's give him a round of applause for acting out
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.11,0:28:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the Kaitō Kid's pitiable end for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.42,0:29:03.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. Kaitō Kid is an expert magician—\Nthe perfect role for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.33,0:29:08.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The two of us do happen to be artists who deceive the eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.26,0:29:09.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Artists?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.70,0:29:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...but I'm a magician by nature. A thief is no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.07,0:29:17.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, then! Please come to the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.64,0:29:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll show you some of my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.28,0:29:24.75,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A phantom thief is a creative artist\Nwho skillfully steals his prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.75,0:29:27.52,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but a detective is nothing more than a critic
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.52,0:29:30.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}who finds fault in what is left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.05,0:29:34.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This sensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.89,0:29:38.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's him! He's somewhere in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.79,0:29:42.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll begin with a simple card trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.20,0:29:46.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on. I've always been the skeptical type.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.70,0:29:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I cut that deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.44,0:29:53.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Certainly. Would any others like to as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.31,0:29:56.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is it?! Who's the Kaitō Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.78,0:29:58.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.35,0:30:01.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They all seem suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.78,0:30:03.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's what she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.72,0:30:09.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The black pearl is with someone especially worthy of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.49,0:30:11.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If only I knew what that meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.66,0:30:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.30,0:30:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.55,0:30:21.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spilled cards won't ruin my luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.55,0:30:21.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}tsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.60,0:30:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moon?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.60,0:30:23.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}tsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.74,0:30:29.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, didn't you have a list of everyone at this party?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.28,0:30:30.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.19,0:30:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.61,0:30:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This? Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.85,0:30:37.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.96,0:30:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.85,0:30:42.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me give you a card in return!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.76,0:30:44.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.76,0:30:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait! First, let me use my X-ray eye to read your minds
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.86,0:30:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and predict your card!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.44,0:30:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.85,0:30:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.31,0:30:59.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.31,0:31:03.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's why he said that in the second letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.11,0:31:05.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've figured it out, Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.58,0:31:08.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The location of your prey, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.59,0:31:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pigeon? Hato? Heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.59,0:31:14.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}hato
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.59,0:31:14.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}hāto
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.96,0:31:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Ace of Hearts, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.46,0:31:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please pick any card you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.93,0:31:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! The right! The right one!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.27,0:31:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"As Caesar was with Cleopatra, I am already by your side."
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.07,0:31:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"—Kaitō Kid"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.88,0:31:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.67,0:31:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.95,0:31:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down, everyone! Confirm your passwords!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.82,0:31:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Nakamori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Don't tell me\Nit's already been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.05,0:31:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he doesn't have it yet, nor has he escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.06,0:31:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's simply confusing us\Nto make things work his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.36,0:31:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, we can catch him! He's not a wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.50,0:32:00.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a human being who relies on tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.18,0:32:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaitō Kid really left a message?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.71,0:32:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep! It was on the card Ran just picked!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.15,0:32:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when and how did he put this in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.79,0:32:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Kid is crafty! Everything about him is a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.86,0:32:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All we know is that he's somewhere in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.40,0:32:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please calm down, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.97,0:32:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean he knows where the real pearl is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.51,0:32:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he did, this is a floating prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.08,0:32:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he possibly make off with the Black Star
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.68,0:32:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with this police presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.10,0:33:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! We'll arrive in Tokyo Harbor in 30 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.00,0:33:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Seal all the exits! Let no one outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.27,0:33:15.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Time to show yourself, Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.24,0:33:19.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is your only chance to strike\Nwhile everyone's restless!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.55,0:33:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran! Where'd your pearl go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.95,0:33:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.42,0:33:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Could someone pick up that pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.30,0:33:35.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.00,0:33:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.36,0:33:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pearl! It exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.27,0:33:43.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me the Kid rigged them!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.01,0:33:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.96,0:33:51.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not wearing this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.78,0:33:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Calm down, everyone! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.76,0:34:03.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.96,0:34:05.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.18,0:34:07.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.30,0:34:10.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Open the door this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.60,0:34:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.30,0:34:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Your pearl is gone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.34,0:34:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Kid! He stole the Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.98,0:34:29.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! So you were wearing the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.32,0:34:32.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! We can't hold them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.26,0:34:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! A large group has gotten out!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.26,0:34:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Kid's with them! Capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.93,0:34:43.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.93,0:34:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}! Let's go catch him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.18,0:34:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.47,0:34:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know who the Kaitō Kid is!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.96,0:35:01.03,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A letter declaring the upcoming theft of the Suzuki family's Black Star
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.03,0:35:02.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}arrived at Sonoko's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.90,0:35:06.00,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The sender was one Kaitō Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.00,0:35:12.04,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Upon cracking his code, I waited for him atop the Haido City Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.04,0:35:14.01,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He landed silently before me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.01,0:35:17.48,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so as not to disturb the stillness of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.48,0:35:19.92,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I only had one chance to use my tranquilizer gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.92,0:35:22.85,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The instant he turned away to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.69,0:35:28.69,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But instead of running, he imitated multiple voices without a machine
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.69,0:35:33.37,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}to lure the police in,\Nand then vanished like smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.37,0:35:36.84,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All that remained was another letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.84,0:35:38.94,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Against Inspector Nakamori's protests,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.94,0:35:44.08,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the Suzuki Industries' 60th anniversary boat party began as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.08,0:35:47.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko's mother, Suzuki Tomoko, devised a plan
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.61,0:35:50.72,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}that looked to spell failure for the Kaitō Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.72,0:35:55.52,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but he blew up the pearls and stole\Nthe Black Star during the confusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.52,0:35:59.39,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've figured out who you are, Kaitō Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.30,0:36:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! You didn't find the Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.77,0:36:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. We checked all the passengers who left the room earlier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.77,0:36:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He has to be on board still! Check every last person on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.68,0:36:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.25,0:36:26.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did he know she was wearing the real Black Star?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.22,0:36:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the engine room, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.39,0:36:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is the Kaitō Kid really in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.23,0:36:43.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}. Do you know about the language of jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.67,0:36:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The language of jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.07,0:36:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pearl means "moon" or "woman."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.47,0:36:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of the passengers on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.72,0:36:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the only woman with moons in her name
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.11,0:36:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is Tomoko Suzuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.18,0:36:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, she had the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.49,0:37:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how does that tell you who the Kid is?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.12,0:37:06.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.46,0:37:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know how the card\Nyou chose had his message?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.33,0:37:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.37,0:37:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a basic trick in which the magician used the pigeon in his right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.47,0:37:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to distract the audience while\Nhe switched decks in his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.31,0:37:29.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the chosen card would be fixed regardless of who cut the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.15,0:37:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if the message was on that card...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.99,0:37:36.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...does that mean Kaitō Kid was that magician?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.92,0:37:42.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! I watched the whole time,\Nbut he never got near the lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.59,0:37:44.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.16,0:37:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's one other person\Nwho could've switched cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.93,0:37:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! That person made them fall,\Npretended to pick them up,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.40,0:37:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then removed a card and added the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.28,0:38:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They hid it in their palm\Nand pretended to pull it from the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.42,0:38:06.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.29,0:38:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or should I say, Kaitō Kid{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.09,0:38:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Chopper #1! He hasn't fled outside!{tune}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.73,0:38:23.54,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is Chopper #2! No suspicious people on deck!{tune}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.54,0:38:27.37,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is Surveillance! Sonar and radar show nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.37,0:38:30.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Keep your eyes peeled!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.21,0:38:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All onboard officers are to split up onto each floor
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.35,0:38:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and capture the Kid on sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.55,0:38:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't let a familiar face fool you!\NHe's a master of disguise!{tune}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.29,0:38:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. You switched places with Ran\Nwhen she left to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.16,0:38:54.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Impressive. I hadn't noticed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.13,0:39:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After becoming Ran, you agitated everyone with your message
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.17,0:39:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and scattered the exploding pearls\Nto cause mass panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.98,0:39:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You then stole the real Black Star\Nduring the confusion
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.08,0:39:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by pretending to prop her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.42,0:39:19.02,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh?! Your pearl is gone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.19,0:39:25.72,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The Kid! He stole the Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.37,0:39:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that you prepared those fireworks means you knew
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.57,0:39:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she had a large number of replicas made.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.64,0:39:37.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quit joking around, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.91,0:39:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know which one was real,\Nand I didn't have any hints!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.48,0:39:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't need hints\Nto know which one was real!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.02,0:39:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once she took her pearl out with a glove, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.92,0:39:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pearls are made of calcium carbonate\Nand are highly reactive to acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.83,0:40:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oil in the fingers would oxidize the surface and make it lose its luster.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.37,0:40:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some people realized, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.08,0:40:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Realized that she'd never give such a delicate jewel to anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.52,0:40:19.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's not enough to—
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.38,0:40:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, that wouldn't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.59,0:40:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But add her dull pearl to the equation and speculation becomes certainty!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.13,0:40:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Just as old pearls in famous museums fade in color over time,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.90,0:40:41.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a pearl's luster lasts a few decades at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.87,0:40:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Black Star was purchased 60 years ago;
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.24,0:40:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it can't possibly look flawless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.61,0:40:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it would have been obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.88,0:40:56.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,once you saw her carefully handle\Nher faded pearl with gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.26,0:41:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk about pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.23,0:41:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was so concerned with you\Nthat I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.53,0:41:10.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wasn't the Black Star\Nin the museum all shiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.94,0:41:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why you didn't take it.\NYou knew it was a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.21,0:41:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you challenged her in your second letter
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.78,0:41:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and told her to bring the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.98,0:41:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even made sure to write "the real one."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.32,0:41:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here! If you suspect me that much,\NI'll call a policeman to—
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.90,0:41:44.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't let you disappear like you did on that roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.47,0:41:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't call for the police that time to spite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.58,0:41:54.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You acted like you were about to hang-glide out,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.11,0:41:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you quickly dressed up as an officer during the flash,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.45,0:42:00.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and hid yourself among them!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.92,0:42:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, it's senseless to ask for help here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.09,0:42:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I set up this one-on-one match out of respect
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.20,0:42:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,for the criminal artist who snuck on board amidst all the security.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.83,0:42:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. Most great artists become famous after they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.81,0:42:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make you a great master, Kaitō Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.28,0:42:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once I place you in the cemetery known as jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.79,0:42:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I surrender. I'll give up on this pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.42,0:42:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell the lady I'm sorry for ruining the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.76,0:42:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now you're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.10,0:42:53.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! The girl I knocked out to get these clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.47,0:42:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll catch cold if we don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.64,0:42:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a perfectionist, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.02,0:43:05.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another flash grenade!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.12,0:43:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.49,0:43:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.93,0:43:17.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.13,0:43:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll get you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.48,0:43:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! There's a girl asleep in this boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.31,0:43:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.68,0:43:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's she doing in here? Anyway, let's get her out...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.69,0:43:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.46,0:43:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Don't take her out! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.19,0:43:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.63,0:43:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"This crimson dress you gave me the other day suits you wonderfully."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.30,0:44:02.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"—The Occasional Dry Cleaner, Kaitō Kid"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.81,0:44:05.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.49,0:44:28.37,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They later found the hang glider Kaitō Kid planned to escape with,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.37,0:44:34.13,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but he, himself, had completely vanished from the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.35,0:46:15.27,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kaito Kid Thwarted!\NGrade-schooler Protects Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.17,0:46:15.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There you are! "Grade-schooler Protects Black Star!"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.27,0:46:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a big hero, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.38,0:46:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, it was just luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.28,0:46:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you guys actually met the Kid!\NYou're so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.58,0:46:27.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Not.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.08,0:46:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what did he look like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.09,0:46:31.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.62,0:46:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.33,0:46:34.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Kid's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.29,0:46:37.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry! He knocked me out too fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.66,0:46:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw his face, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.72,0:46:42.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of older man was he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.17,0:46:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was surprisingly young.\NIn his twenties, or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.94,0:46:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't give me your cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.44,0:46:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Falling into the ocean while touring the Selizabeth! Talk about stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.11,0:46:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.72,0:47:04.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's that brat's fault!\NSwimming away was my only option!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.46,0:47:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! That high-schooler...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.33,0:47:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't he look like Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.63,0:47:10.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.93,0:47:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe the guy you saw in Shibuya was...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.64,0:47:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.34,0:47:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's good to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.97,0:47:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.84,0:47:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mitsuaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! What's going on?!\NMitsuaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.83,0:47:45.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Mitsuaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.86,0:47:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's there. Down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.66,0:47:57.66,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.66,0:48:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Great Detective of the West
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.85,0:48:04.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The next episode airs October 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.67,0:48:07.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Fuu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Ryo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Hazuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, wait for me!
